porangi
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:2
Definition:mad, insane; foolish, imbecilic
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: ca1900 Jane Morison, Marlborough (perhaps adopted from a stay in Taumaranui timber camps)
